stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Processing : Message sent
    Processing --> OllamaCall : Call LLM
    OllamaCall --> LLMResponse : Success
    OllamaCall --> Fallback : Ollama offline
    LLMResponse --> Idle : Response displayed
    Fallback --> EnhancedMode : Use rule-based
    EnhancedMode --> Idle : Fallback displayed